                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18620818-891-offence-1 t18620818-name-499"></join>Charles Stratton</persName>, and stealing therein 2 coats, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., and other articles, value together 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., his property; to which</rs>
