                        <interp inst="t18620818-891-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">John Smith was further charged with having been before convicted at West<lb></lb>minster, in October, 1859, in the name of <persName id="t18620818-name-503">
                        <interp inst="t18620818-name-503" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>John Thomas</persName>; to which he</hi>
